    "patch_code": "private static class PropertiesTypeBuilder : TypeBuilderBase\n\t{\n\tpublic propertiesTypeBuilder()\n\t{ super(Map.class); }\n\tpublic Type buildType(TypeConverter registry, Class<?> type)\n\t{\n\t\tif (!type.isAssigned()) return null;\n\t\t\n\t// ` properties` is special - it always has two types\n\tif (!type.isAssignableFrom(Map.class)) return null;\n\t\n\t// now let's figure out types of types...\n\tList<Type> types = findType parameters(type,Map.class);\n\tif types.size() == 2 return types[0].getType();\n\treturn null;\n\t}\n\t}\n\t\t\n\ttypeMapper._Builder._addBuilder(new propertiesTypeBuilder());",
